creator: Vesync
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to VeSync!

By signing up, you’re starting on your journey toward a healthier, happier life. Build a smart home today by connecting your VeSync-enabled product, and join our millions of users around the world.

Connect Your Home
Control your home from anywhere by connecting all of your devices through the VeSync app.

Crush Your Goals
Track your nutrition, set fitness goals, and share your progress with other users.

Better Together
Exchange tips, ask questions, and get the latest updates from our online community.

Member-Exclusive Deals

Connect Your Home

title: VeSync

creator: Vesync
descriptionHtml:
VeSync is an all-in-one app that helps you build a smart, healthy life. With VeSync, you can take control of your smart home devices, create a healthy living space, manage your weight and diet, and gain support from the community. Whether you're looking to simplify your daily life or optimize your wellness journey, VeSync has got you covered.

To get started, here are some ways to help you make the most of your VeSync experience:

Connect Your Home
Control your home from anywhere by connecting all of your devices through the VeSync app.

Crush Your Goals
Plan your diet, track your meals and health data, exercise regularly, and build healthy habits to reach your health goals.

Better Together
Exchange tips, ask questions, and get the latest updates from our online community.

Member-Exclusive Deals
Shop all your favorites and get member-exclusive discounts in the VeSync store.

Have questions? No problem. We’re here to help support@vesync.com.
* VeSync has connected to Apple’s HealthKit platform, and can now feed health and wellness data into Apple Health.
* Some products and features may not be available in all regions. Compatible devices required.
* For the best experience, download the latest version of the app, and make sure your firmware is updated.
* VeSync Fit has been upgraded to VeSync, we will continue to provide you with a better experience.

5.0.60

creator: Vesync
descriptionHtml:
VeSync is an all-in-one app that helps you build a smart, healthy life. With VeSync, you can take control of your smart home devices, create a healthy living space, manage your weight and diet, and gain support from the community. Whether you're looking to simplify your daily life or optimize your wellness journey, VeSync has got you covered.

To get started, here are some ways to help you make the most of your VeSync experience:

Connect Your Home
Control your home from anywhere by connecting all of your devices through the VeSync app.

Crush Your Goals
Plan your diet, track your meals and health data, exercise regularly, and build healthy habits to reach your health goals.

Better Together
Exchange tips, ask questions, and get the latest updates from our online community.

Member-Exclusive Deals
Shop all your favorites and get member-exclusive discounts in the VeSync store.

Have questions? No problem. We’re here to help support@vesync.com.
* VeSync has connected to Apple’s HealthKit platform, and can now feed health and wellness data into Apple Health.
* Some products and features may not be available in all regions. Compatible devices required.
* For the best experience, download the latest version of the app, and make sure your firmware is updated.
* VeSync Fit has been upgraded to VeSync, we will continue to provide you with a better experience.
